trans-unit.source: You must be logged in to save a blueprint

Hi! I created this website after playing Oyxgen not included for a while, browsing the subreddits and forums for the game. One thing I noticed is that when sharing their builds, people usually share a bunch of imgur pictures with the different overlays. This is fine for simple builds, but you can't very well zoom in, switch overlays, look what the setting is on that buffer logic switch... So I decided to create a tool where players could either upload the builds they created in game, or create their build from scratch on the web page. Here are some current features of the website : You can build your blueprint from scratch using the various toolsYou can import templates from the game (more on that later)You can cycle between various overlays. each overlay will hightlight different buildingsYou can save your blueprintsYou can share your blueprints, by exporting png images for each overlayOr by sharing a link that will directly open your blueprint! click here to open my SPOM in a new tab!
trans-unit.target: 嗨！我在玩了一段时间的《缺氧》，并浏览了它的 subreddit 和论坛之后创建了这个网站。在浏览这些网站的时候，我注意到了一件事——人们在分享他们的建筑模块时，通常会用一堆 Imgur 图片展示不同概览下的模块截图。对于比较简单的模块，这个方法还比较适用。但是，用这种方法不能把图片放得很大，也不能轻松切换概览，更不能查看缓冲门的时长设置……因此，我决定创建一个小工具——玩家们可以用它上传游戏中的模块，也可以直接在网站上用它建造模块。下面列举了本网站的一些现有特性：可以用各种工具从头建造一个蓝图可以从游戏中直接导入模板（后文有详细信息）可以在不同概览间来回切换，不同的概览下会高亮显示不同的建筑可以保存蓝图可以通过导出各概览的 png 图片来分享蓝图或者直接用链接分享！点击这里可以在新标签页查看我的电解制氧模块！

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, you can use the arrow keys to move the camera by one tile in the direction of the arrow
